quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  18,79,"“Sano chombochila, basi chaliji chaŵandu ŵakulaga ŵakamula masengo m’mbwani, ninasachile kuti nachipe ayibu, sano paujo pao paliji pana mwenye juŵaliji nkujigala chombo chilichose (chambone) mwakotosya.”"
  18,80,"“Sano kanchanda kala, nikuti achinangolo ŵakwe ŵaliji ŵakulupilila, basi nitwajogwepe kuti atakwakanganichisya kutenda yakusumba mpika ni yaukafili.”"
  18,81,"“Nitwasachile kuti Ambuje ŵao ŵatindanichisye ni jwambone kumpunda jwele pakutakata ni jwakuŵandichila nnope ku chanasa (chakwatendela achinangolo ŵakwe).”"
  19,40,"Chisimu Uwwe ni ŵatuchitawalila litaka ni yaili palakwepo (yosope ichiŵa Yetuwe panyuma pakuwa iwumbe yosope), soni Kukwetu tachiuchisyidwa."
  19,41,"Soni munsalani Ibrahima m’Chitabu (achi cha Qur’an), chisimu jwalakwe jwaliji jwakuŵecheta yakuona soni Ntume."
  19,42,"Pandema jaŵatite kwa babagwe: “E baba ŵangu! Ligongo chichi nkugalagatila chindu changapikana, changalola soni changaŵa nkunkamuchisya chilichose?”"
  20,22,"“Soni kwapatisyani ligasa lyenu kungwapa kwenu; chilikopoche lili lyeswela (lyakumelemenda) ngaŵaga mwaulwele, (chele nikuŵa) chisimosimo chine.”"
  20,23,"“Kuti tunnosye ine mu isimosimo Yetu yekulungwakulungwa.”"
  20,24,"“Jaawulani kwa Firiauna, chisimu jwalakwejo jusumbile mpika (pakulikwesya).”"